Interface IEventContext

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IConfigResourceEventContext, IConfigServiceEventContext, IConfigStoreEventContext, IFileEventContext, IRankedServiceEventContext<S>

    public interface IEventContext
    Implementations of this interface provide context information for events. This approach is preferred in the public API, instead of extending the Event class itself.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies
